@@ -5,6 +5,31 @@ All notable changes to this project are documented here.
 The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
 and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
 
+## [0.2.2] - 2026-05-27
+
+Bug-fix and test-tooling release. Under `0.x`, non-breaking changes increment
+the patch version. This implements the strategy documented by ADR-0001 in 0.2.1.
+
+### Fixed
+
+- **Rank drops are no longer hidden.** In the keyword table, a lost ranking
+  (`prev < now`) previously rendered identically to no-change (`—`), masking
+  declines from users. Drops now render `↓ N` in `text-danger`, while gains keep
+  `↑ N` in `text-success` and flat stays `—` (`src/features/rankings/components/KeywordTable.tsx`).
+
+### Added
+
+- **Test harness.** New `npm test` script running `node --import tsx --test`
+  over `src/**/*.test.ts` (`tsx` added as a devDependency).
+- **Pure rank-delta logic** extracted into `src/features/rankings/rank.ts`
+  (`rankDelta()` / `formatRankDelta()`, non-finite-safe), with 27 passing unit
+  tests across `rank.test.ts` and `src/lib/format.test.ts`.
+
+### Changed
+
+- **`KeywordTable`** refactored to consume the pure `rank.ts` helpers instead of
+  computing the delta inline.
+
 ## [0.2.1] - 2026-05-27
 
 Documentation-only release. No runtime, dependency, or API changes — under `0.x`,
